        //-     for css or javascript files to access as long as the css & js file(s)
        //-     are imported like above in #5. Javascript and CSS both can change the
        //-     the style of the DOM (Document Object Model) but that is the only thing CSS can do.
        //-     Javascript is able to access and modify all the contents of the DOM.
        header(class="container_row_1" id="header") 
